Grammar

    0 $accept: program $end

    1 program: exp

    2 exp: assignexp

    3 assignexp: lvalue ASSIGN assignexp
    4          | orexp

    5 orexp: andexp ortail

    6 ortail: /* empty */
    7       | OR andexp ortail

    8 andexp: relexp andtail

    9 andtail: /* empty */
   10        | AND relexp andtail

   11 relexp: addexp reltail

   12 reltail: /* empty */
   13        | relop addexp

   14 relop: EQ
   15      | NEQ
   16      | LT
   17      | LE
   18      | GT
   19      | GE

   20 addexp: mulexp addtail

   21 addtail: /* empty */
   22        | PLUS mulexp addtail
   23        | MINUS mulexp addtail

   24 mulexp: unaryexp multail

   25 multail: /* empty */
   26        | TIMES unaryexp multail
   27        | DIVIDE unaryexp multail

   28 unaryexp: MINUS unaryexp
   29         | atomexp

   30 atomexp: NIL
   31        | INT
   32        | STRING
   33        | BREAK
   34        | LPAREN explist_opt RPAREN
   35        | idexp
   36        | IF exp THEN exp
   37        | IF exp THEN exp ELSE exp
   38        | WHILE exp DO exp
   39        | FOR ID ASSIGN exp TO exp DO exp
   40        | LET decs_opt IN explist_opt END

   41 idexp: ID idsuffix

   42 lvalue: ID lvaluetail

   43 idsuffix: /* empty */
   44         | LPAREN args_opt RPAREN
   45         | LBRACE recfields_opt RBRACE
   46         | lvstart

   47 lvstart: DOT ID lvaluetail
   48        | LBRACK exp RBRACK subsuffix

   49 subsuffix: OF exp
   50          | lvaluetail

   51 lvaluetail: /* empty */
   52           | DOT ID lvaluetail
   53           | LBRACK exp RBRACK lvaluetail

   54 explist_opt: /* empty */
   55            | explist

   56 explist: exp
   57        | explist SEMICOLON exp

   58 args_opt: /* empty */
   59         | args

   60 args: exp
   61     | args COMMA exp

   62 recfields_opt: /* empty */
   63              | recfields

   64 recfields: recfield
   65          | recfields COMMA recfield

   66 recfield: ID EQ exp

   67 decs_opt: /* empty */
   68         | decs

   69 decs: dec
   70     | decs dec

   71 dec: typedec
   72    | vardec
   73    | fundec

   74 typedec: TYPE ID EQ ty

   75 vardec: VAR ID ASSIGN exp
   76       | VAR ID COLON ID ASSIGN exp

   77 fundec: FUNCTION ID LPAREN tyfields_opt RPAREN EQ exp
   78       | FUNCTION ID LPAREN tyfields_opt RPAREN COLON ID EQ exp

   79 ty: ID
   80   | LBRACE tyfields_opt RBRACE
   81   | ARRAY OF ID

   82 tyfields_opt: /* empty */
   83             | tyfields

   84 tyfields: tyfield
   85         | tyfields COMMA tyfield

   86 tyfield: ID COLON ID


